<text>Lichtspielhaus (obsolete German for &quot;cinema&quot;; literally &quot;light-play house&quot;) is the second DVD by German Neue Deutsche Härte band Rammstein, released on 1 December 2003. It is a compilation of all their videos until then, and some live performances, commercial advertisements, trailers and makings-of features.

