* 1981: Grand Prix National de la Photographie
* 1982: Hasselblad Award
* 2003: Lifetime Achievement Award from the Lucie Awards
* 2006: Prix Nadar for the photobook &quot;Henri Cartier-Bresson: Scrapbook&quot;

