<doc id="406214" wikidata="Q5909743" url="?curid=406214" title="Hot Anger Soon Cold">
<text>Hot Anger Soon Cold is a play written by Henry Chettle, Henry Porter and Ben Jonson. No extant copies of the play are known.

The play is mentioned in Philip Henslowe&#x27;s diary for August 1598. On 18 August, the authors were paid £6 for the script by the Admiral&#x27;s Men.

