<doc id="406225" wikidata="Q7766480" url="?curid=406225" title="The Stepmother's Tragedy">
<text>The Stepmother&#x27;s Tragedy is a play written by Henry Chettle and Thomas Dekker. It is mentioned in Philip Henslowe&#x27;s diary in August 1599. No extant copies of the play are known.

